  "original_title": "\u0dc4\u0dd9\u0daf\u0dd2\u0dba\u0d9a \u0db4\u0db8\u0dab \u0db1\u0ddc\u0dc0 \u0db1\u0dd4\u0db9 \u0daf\u0dd2\u0dbb\u0dd2\u0db8\u0dad\u0dca      \u0db8\u0dc0\u0d9a\u0dd2",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Not just a nurse, you are an encouraging mother",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "This morning we met by chance by a nurse who came to the Padaviya Base Hospital on a bicycle after covering a distance of 20-25 km, challenging the fuel shortage.",
        "Padavi - From Sri Pura to Palugaswanguwa, Aliwanguwa, D10 Maithripalapura, C Yaya.",
        "The young nurse expressed some reluctance to appear in the media. However, when inquired from her, she stated that although she had arrived on a motorbike the previous day, she had started working on a bicycle from today due to a severe shortage of petrol.",
        "When we inquired about this from the Medical Superintendent of Padaviya Base Hospital, he said that all the staff of his institution, including the nurses and doctors, have been severely inconvenienced."
      ],
